metadata.name: Gone Phishing #1/10
metadata.description:
On February 19th, 2022, some OpenSea users fell victim to a phishing attack. 

A cultural cartoon of the times. This cartoon, created by Jeff Cole, pays homage to the upcoming release of Space Doodles while showing the world the NFT space isnâ€™t always sunshine and rainbows. 

This event raised a lot of concern as hackers were able to gain access to users wallets and take their JPEGs hostage. Above the surface, it may look like smooth seas, but these vulnerabilities shows no ship is safe as we sail forward.
